{"tid":968442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嫦娥首登月背 玉兔傳回近照 將展三大任務 揭開神秘面紗","createTime":"2019-01-04T08:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T10:22:01.000Z","uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"574725003444d1b5fa8779d2d89ccb99d1649a31","tid":968442,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T08:40:32.000Z","msg":"厲害了,我的國<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n昨日10時26分，嫦娥四號探測器在月球背面南極-艾特肯盆地內的馮卡門撞擊坑內，實現人類第一次在月球背面着陸，並傳回首張「近照」，揭開這片未被探測之地的的神秘面紗。此次任務也實現了人類首次月背與地球的中繼通訊，嫦娥四號和月球車「玉兔二號」將一同展開低頻射電天文觀測、月球背面巡視與結構研究，以及中子輻射劑量、中性原子等月球環境探測的三大任務。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/article/20190104/s00013/1546540174769/%E5%AB%A6%E5%A8%A5%E9%A6%96%E7%99%BB%E6%9C%88%E8%83%8C-%E7%8E%89%E5%85%94%E5%82%B3%E5%9B%9E%E8%BF%91%E7%85%A7-%E5%B0%87%E5%B1%95%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99-%E6%8F%AD%E9%96%8B%E7%A5%9E%E7%A7%98%E9%9D%A2%E7%B4%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2Farticle%2F20190104%2Fs00013%2F1546540174769%2F%25E5%25AB%25A6%25E5%25A8%25A5%25E9%25A6%2596%25E7%2599%25BB%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%2583%258C-%25E7%258E%2589%25E5%2585%2594%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%259B%259E%25E8%25BF%2591%25E7%2585%25A7-%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%25B1%2595%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%258B%2599-%25E6%258F%25AD%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%25A5%259E%25E7%25A7%2598%25E9%259D%25A2%25E7%25B4%2597&d=tHpTv%2Byl%2BAvHyGucOEPNII9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=7fb51ebb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2Farticle%2F20190104%2Fs00013%2F1546540174769%2F%25E5%25AB%25A6%25E5%25A8%25A5%25E9%25A6%2596%25E7%2599%25BB%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%2583%258C-%25E7%258E%2589%25E5%2585%2594%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%259B%259E%25E8%25BF%2591%25E7%2585%25A7-%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%25B1%2595%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%258B%2599-%25E6%258F%25AD%